description: Perform object detection on images using JigsawStack's Object Detection Model, capable of image grounding, segmentation and computer use.

api_key.info: Your JigsawStack API key for authentication

prompts.info: The prompts to ground the object detection model. You can pass a list of comma-separated prompts to extract different information from the image.

url.info: The image URL. Not required if file_store_key is specified.

file_store_key.info: The key used to store the image on JigsawStack File Storage. Not required if url is specified.

annotated_image.info: If true, will return a URL for annotated image with detected objects.

features.info: Select the features to enable for object detection

return_type.info: Select the return type for the object detection results such as masks or annotations.

errors.import_error: JigsawStack package not found. Please install it using: pip install jigsawstack>=0.2.7
errors.invalid_prompt: Prompt must be a list of strings or a single string
errors.missing_image_source: Either URL or File Store Key must be provided to perform object detection

logs.detection_complete: Object detection complete - {count} object(s) detected, Annotated image: {has_annotated}
logs.detection_success: Object detection completed successfully - {count} object(s) found.
